Redis cluster is a shared redis setup for high availablity and high relability

Redis Cluster

16000 hashes available in redis cluster


M - S
M - S
M - S

16000 /  No of master

if master goes down the slave of the master will become the master

creating a cluster

1. create 6 instace of redis server with some config values copied from ipanther repo .
2. start all 6 instance using redis server <config>
3. redis-cli --cluster create <ip address> <ip address> <ip address> <ip address> <ip address>  


